data.description: Welcome to your beautiful 5-bedroom home! This magnificent home boasts generous living spaces, making it ideal for families or those who love to entertain. The open concept layout creates a hub for social gatherings and family bonding. The large kitchen has beautiful granite counters, tons of cabinet space, new dishwasher and stainless steel appliances. The grand master suite includes a large walk-in closet, en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub, dual vanities, and a separate shower. Upstairs you have 4 additional bedrooms to accomodate all your families' needs along with an oversized gameroom to enjoy. This home is in the highly acclaimed Lamar ISD and boasts great schools. It's close to shopping, grocery stores and many excellent restaurants! Great place to raise a family and call it home. THIS IS A MUST SEE!
